name: Custom Bic Lighters (5 Pack)
description:
Engrave your artwork or personalized message onto disposable Bic lighters. We're pretty capable of putting whatever images you want as long as its as close to line art as possible (pictures are kinda tricky on these ones!). 

Want 5 black lighters? No problem. Wanna mix & match? No problem. We'll contact you after you place your order to see which ones you'd like.

Available Lighter Colors:

Black
White
Red
Blue
Yellow
Green
Brown
Orange

Available Paint Colors: (Yes these are hand painted!)

Black
White
Silver
Gold
Copper
Amethyst
Turquoise
Sapphire
Emerald
Jade


For examples of what to expect please visit our page titled "Bic Gallery"

How to Send Over Your Custom Image

After check-out, you will be contacted by one of our designers.
They will provide instructions on how to upload your image. If all is good, we engrave the image onto the lighter and ship it right out to you! 

Although we do not censor any custom designs, all submissions are subject to review.

Do not submit Copyrighted or Trademarked images which you do not hold the rights to. Absolutely no Sport Team Logos, Registered Trademarks, Cartoon Characters, Rap Group Logos etc.
